com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.math

Class RightShiftArithmetic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.math.MathOperationShift
      • com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.math.RightShiftArithmetic

  • public class RightShiftArithmetic
extends MathOperationShift
    This class performs a right unsigned/arithmetic shift operations for integer plate stacks, plates, wells and well sets. Right shift operations can also be performed on a subset of data using a beginning index and subset length.
    Author:
    Jesse L. Mull
